name: Factom Status
body:
### Factom Status
We will keep this page up showing the status of the Factom system.

At this time it is a manual process, so there may be some delay between finding a problem and posting it here.

You might also want to check the [Issues](https://github.com/FactomProject/WorkItems/issues) page to see if someone has been assigned to fix it.

# Factom is currently **Up**.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
